2007-02-28  Hans Utz  <hutz@owl>

	* utils/logPlayer/LogPlayer.cpp:
	adding -? output for command line option -event_channel

	* examples/videoFilter2/Makefile.am, idl/Makefile.am, performance-tests/logging/Makefile.am, performance-tests/nmc/Makefile.am:
	removing deprecated and redundant options from the tao_idl command line.
	changing the LD_LIBRARY_PATH setting for tao_idl, hoping it works better.
	this make Miro compile with TAO 1.5.6, apart from a configure-problem
	when trying to look up the ACE/TAO build options

	TODO: unite the tao_idl rule in Make-rules (?) add a IDLFLAGS for allowing
	to inject additional flags to the tao_idl command line

