	monster commit touching almost every file of the repository:
	installing new file headers, that better reflect the licensing, to avoid
	confusion.

2007-02-21  Coyote  <coyote@owl>

	* etc/gonzales.xml, etc/roadrunner.xml:  :-) akt cam parameters

2007-02-16  Coyote  <coyote@owl>

	* src/faulMotor/FaulMotorConnection.cpp:
	debug:  the frist motorsetting after motordisabling had wrong prevSpeed

2007-02-13  Gerd Mayer  <gmayer@owl>

	* idl/Makefile.am:
	do not override the set LD_LIBRARY_PATH, instead append the necessary entries

2007-02-02  Gerd Mayer  <gmayer@owl>

	* idl/.cvsignore: beautify cvs

	* utils/widgets/SimpleParameter.cpp, utils/widgets/SimpleParameter.h, utils/widgets/SimpleParameterEdit.cpp, utils/widgets/SimpleParameterEdit.h:
	add support for new enum-style data types

	- comboboxes for "1 from n"
	- listboxes for "m from n"

	* src/miro/.cvsignore: beautify cvs

	* src/miro/Enumeration.cpp, src/miro/Enumeration.h, src/miro/EnumerationMultiple.cpp, src/miro/EnumerationMultiple.h, src/miro/Makefile.am, src/miro/XmlParse.cpp, src/miro/XmlParse.h, src/params/Parser.cpp, src/params/Parser.h:
	- add support for two new data types supported in the miro configuration framework:
	-- an enumeration style "1 from n" helper class: Enumeration
	-- and an extended "m from n" class: EnumerationMultiple (okay, okay, it's a dumb name)

	use it like this:

	<config_item name="TESTIT" parent="Miro::Config" final="false">
	  <config_parameter name="type1" type="Miro::Enumeration" values="VAL1 VAL2 VAL4 VAL5" default="VAL3" />
	  <config_parameter name="type2" type="Miro::EnumerationMultiple" values="VAL1 VAL2 VAL3 VAL4 VAL5" default="VAL3 VAL4" />
	  <config_parameter name="type3" type="string" default="Value" />
	</config_item>

	mainly preparation for the umcoming changes in the VIP config stuff, but might be useful also, when only a given set of values can be used (e.g. the interpolation method in image scaling...)

	* utils/widgets/ParameterList.cpp, utils/widgets/ParameterListDialog.cpp:
	and again... makes debugging considerably easier

	* utils/widgets/DeferredParameterEdit.cpp, utils/widgets/DocumentXML.cpp:
	again, throw exception instead of qstring

	* utils/widgets/CompoundParameter.cpp:
	throw miro exception instead of qstring

2007-01-30  Hans Utz  <hutz@owl>

	* src/miro/LogReader.cpp:
	Fixing log-reader TAO-version cascade for the OCI 1.4a release of TAO.
	Thanks to Greg for coding it.

2007-01-25  Coyote  <coyote@owl>

	* idl/Makefile.am: *** empty log message ***

2007-01-13  Hans Utz  <hutz@owl>

	* config/Make-rules, idl/Makefile.am:
	- adding rpath for ACE/TAO libraries
	- explicitly stating the LD_LIBRARY_PATH for tao_idl.
	  tao_idl does not use rpath. this way we should find the libraries
	  independently of this environment variable.

	* COPYING:
	switching the license to LGPL as announced/discussed on the mailing list

