2006-03-24  Gerd Mayer  <gmayer@owl>

	* bin/.cvsignore: beautify cvs

	* Makefile.am:
	stop creating this annoying idl->. link in idl. I think we do not need this (oehm, correct me if I'm wrong :-)

	distclean targets are handled more elegant.

	* all.h.sh, config/conditionals.m4:
	precompiled headers should now work even if srcdir != builddir (still does not work together with distCC)

	* config/Make-rules: silence the local installation procedure

	* doc/html/Makefile.am, doc/html/doxygen.cpp.in, doc/html/doxygen.idl.in, doc/tex/Makefile.am:
	Change the way, how documentation is made, significantly. It now recognizes dependencies correctly, which means, both directories are only built if either the respective tex-files or the source files (on which the html docu relies) are changed. This means especially, that it is not built again during a "make install". As a nice side-effect, it is removed on "make uninstall" also.

	* scripts/Makefile.am:
	do not install scripts, as they are only useful for development... (if at all)

	* pch/Makefile.am:
	do not install dummy-library locally and during "make install". overall header file is now cleaned during "make distclean"

	* examples/b21Motion/Makefile.am, examples/params/Makefile.am, examples/videoFilter/Makefile.am, examples/videoFilter2/Makefile.am, botsvcs/tests/BAP/dynamicPolicy/Makefile.am, botsvcs/tests/BAP/engine/Makefile.am, botsvcs/tests/BAP/lib/Makefile.am, botsvcs/tests/BAP/parsing/Makefile.am, botsvcs/tests/BAP/priorityArbiter/Makefile.am, botsvcs/examples/BAP/b21/Makefile.am, botsvcs/examples/BAP/engine/Makefile.am, botsvcs/examples/BAP/rangeSensor/Makefile.am, botsvcs/examples/BAP/simple/Makefile.am:
	do not install these examples locally and during "make install".

	* templates/features_miro.m4: remove old stuff

	* config/conditionals.m4, configure.ac:
	miro-config now outputs the correct libdc1394 library used... import for derived projects

	* src/video/Makefile.am: forgot to remove stuff in this makefile

	* tests/panTilt/.cvsignore: beautify CVS output

	* bin/.cvsignore: beautify CVS ouput

	* config/Make-rules, config/conditionals.m4, examples/video/Makefile.am, examples/videoFilter/Makefile.am, examples/videoFilter2/Makefile.am, src/video/BufferManager1394.cpp, src/video/BufferManager1394.h, src/video/Makefile.am, src/video/VideoDevice1394.cpp, src/video/VideoDevice1394.h:
