2005-11-29  Rebecca Fay  <rfay@owl>

	* utils/qtTouchPad/MainForm.h:
	The KickerC.h file is only created if --enable-Sparrow99 is selected
	on the configure; i.e. it isn't created with the --disable-Sparrow 99
	option.
	So, added an #ifdef block around the include.
	Please, try not to break existing code for the "not Sparrows" users.
	(Test before commiting, or just after that)
	Guillem.

