2005-08-05  Guillem Pages  <guillem@owl>

	* tests/fusedRangeSensor/.cvsignore: Oops, forgot something ;-)

	* bin/.cvsignore, configure.ac, idl/.cvsignore, idl/FusedRangeSensor.idl, idl/Makefile.am, src/Makefile.am, src/fusedRangeSensor/.cvsignore, src/fusedRangeSensor/FusedRangeSensor.cpp, src/fusedRangeSensor/FusedRangeSensor.h, src/fusedRangeSensor/FusedRangeSensorImpl.cpp, src/fusedRangeSensor/FusedRangeSensorImpl.h, src/fusedRangeSensor/Makefile.am, src/fusedRangeSensor/Parameters.xml, tests/Makefile.am, tests/fusedRangeSensor/FusedRangeSensorTest.cpp, tests/fusedRangeSensor/Makefile.am, tests/fusedRangeSensor/README:
	Added a derived range sensor, which fuses other range sensors into a
	 single sensor (Fused).
	Currently it chooses the minimum of the n values for a given angle.
	Values not provided by any sensor can be either masked or interpolated.

	* examples/player/pioneers.world: Ordered robots by id

