	Solved an incoherence in the sonar simulation. XML said 8 values and ReactorTask
	 worked with 16. Now it's everything sweet sixteen ;-) Actually, XML is 16 and
	 ReactorTask reads the value from the Player Proxy.
	Also removed some unused code.

