	- opend up a botsvcs directory for high level services and frameworks
	- moved the BAP stuff into this directory
	- moved the BAP stuff into its own namespace Miro::BAP
	- added the ability for hierarchic policy modelling
	- reworked external transition handling

2005-03-30  speedy  <speedy@owl>

	* src/sparrow/SparrowConnection2003.cpp, src/sparrow/SparrowEventHandler2003.cpp:
	fixing delayed pan ticks query
	the ticks as reported from the tiny are written to cerr on log level 5

2005-03-30  Hans Utz  <hutz@owl>

	* src/sparrow/Parameters.xml, src/sparrow/SparrowConnection2003.cpp, src/sparrow/SparrowConnection2003.h, src/sparrow/SparrowConsumer2003.cpp:
	new pan operation mode:
	the ticks per degree are now located in the config file and are not
	taken from the tiny message. the message is just reported for manual update
	make sure, that the pan finished calibration on startup before starting
	SparrowBase or NixPlayer

	the benefit is, that we do not have to wait for half a minute after startup

