2005-03-17  Guillem Pages  <guillem@owl>

	* etc/PlayerDefault.xml: Added some defaults for the camera parameters

	* etc/SparrowDefault.xml, etc/coyote.xml, etc/gonzales.xml, etc/passtnix.xml, etc/roadrunner.xml, etc/rosita.xml, etc/speedy.xml, etc/trifftnix.xml:
	Added the pan range parameters to the sparrows xml files. Currently
	 -90 <-> 90. Should be changed for the new pan units.

	* configure.ac, etc/PpbDefault.xml, etc/eve.xml, idl/.cvsignore, idl/CameraControl.idl, idl/CanonCamera.idl, idl/CanonCameraControl.idl, idl/Makefile.am, src/miro/CameraControlImpl.cpp, src/miro/CameraControlImpl.h, src/miro/Makefile.am, src/miro/PanImpl.cpp, src/miro/PanImpl.h, src/miro/PanTiltImpl.cpp, src/miro/PanTiltImpl.h, src/miro/SvcParameters.xml, src/miro/TiltImpl.cpp, src/miro/TiltImpl.h, src/panTilt/DpPanTilt.cpp, src/panTilt/DpPanTilt.h, src/panTilt/PanTiltImpl.cpp, src/panTilt/PanTiltImpl.h, src/pioneer/CanonCameraControlImpl.cpp, src/pioneer/CanonCameraControlImpl.h, src/pioneer/CanonCameraImpl.h, src/pioneer/CanonDevice.h, src/pioneer/CanonPanTiltImpl.cpp, src/pioneer/CanonPanTiltImpl.h, src/pioneer/Makefile.am, src/pioneer/Parameters.xml, src/pioneerBase/PioneerBase.cpp, src/pioneerBase/PioneerBase.h, src/playerBase/PlayerBase.cpp, src/playerBase/PlayerBase.h, src/playerBase/PlayerPanTiltImpl.cpp, src/playerBase/PlayerPanTiltImpl.h, src/sparrow/SparrowPanTiltImpl.cpp, src/sparrow/SparrowPanTiltImpl.h, src/sparrowBase/SparrowBase.cpp, src/sparrowBase/SparrowServer.cpp, src/sparrowBase/SparrowServer.h, tests/panTilt/PanTiltTest.cpp, tests/pioneer/PioneerTest.cpp:
	Added dummy Pan, Tilt and PanTilt classes w/ implementations, and made
	 the real devices inherit from the corresponding ones.
	Added Pan and Tilt parameters to the Service Parameters xml file.

	Added a new generic interface "CameraControl" to control zoom, focus,
	 shutter, ... parameters on cameras.
	Added a "CanonCameraControl" interface for canon cameras and set the old
	 "CanonCamera" to deprecated.
	The new interface measures Zoom in horizontal angle, and Focus in mm; not
	 in percentage anymore.

	Set the (by now) corract parameters on PpbDefault.xml and eve.xml

	Added a MIRO_HAS_DEPRECATED constant in Miro/config.h. Sorry, that
	 means BOOTSTRAP

	I probably forgot something besides testing, but now I don't know what.
	Will make the changes if (when) needed.

