	* src/playerBase/Makefile.am, src/playerBase/PlayerBase.cpp, src/playerBase/PlayerBase.h, src/playerBase/PlayerPanTiltImpl.cpp:
	Swapped axis for PanTilt (Pan & Tilt moved the wrong way wrt Miro standard)
	Reading Laser::Parameters for laser instead of generic robot parameters (might change again in the future)
	Really reading the value of cameraUpsideDown instead of assuming false

	* idl/Makefile.am, src/Makefile.am:
	Moved laser from b21dirs to globaldirs, as Player also uses it and there has been reports of a Pioneer with a SICK laser scanner.
	Should not slow the compilation much (there are not so many files)

	* src/playerBase/PlayerPanTiltImpl.cpp, src/playerBase/PlayerPanTiltImpl.h:
	Ups, forgot to add those files on check-in.
	Pan Tilt implementation for the Player interface.

