2005-01-17  speedy  <speedy@owl>

	* src/video/BufferManager.cpp, src/video/BufferManager.h, src/video/BufferManager1394.cpp, src/video/BufferManager1394.h, src/video/BufferManagerBTTV.cpp, src/video/BufferManagerBTTV.h, src/video/BufferManagerMeteor.cpp, src/video/BufferManagerMeteor.h, src/video/BufferManagerQuickCam.cpp, src/video/BufferManagerQuickCam.h:
