	* src/params/Generator.cpp, src/params/Generator.h, src/params/Parameter.cpp, src/params/Parameter.h, src/params/Parser.cpp, src/params/Parser.h, src/params/Type.cpp, src/params/Type.h:
	making ACE_Sched_Params known to the parameter file parsers
	- adding flag for additional include
	work on the parameter handling for advanced parameter features
	- the sets members are now displayable in the order of declaration
	  instead of alphabetically
	- the inheritance of types is queryable
	  this is done for polymorphic reference types
	  would be a cool feature for filter tree declarations, but the widgets
	  can't do it by now

