	* src/sparrow/Makefile.am, src/sparrowBase/Makefile.am, src/speech/Makefile.am, src/sphinx/Makefile.am, src/video/Makefile.am, tests/b21/Makefile.am, tests/dpPanTilt/Makefile.am, tests/dtlk/Makefile.am, tests/faul/Makefile.am, tests/gripper/Makefile.am, tests/kicker/Makefile.am, tests/log/Makefile.am, tests/motion/Makefile.am, tests/notify/Makefile.am, tests/notifyMulticast/Makefile.am, tests/odometry/Makefile.am, tests/panTilt/Makefile.am, tests/pioneer/Makefile.am, tests/rangeSensor/Makefile.am, tests/sparrow/Makefile.am, tests/speech/Makefile.am, tests/sphinx/Makefile.am, tests/video/Makefile.am, tests/videoBroker/Makefile.am, tests/xml/Makefile.am, utils/Joystick/Makefile.am, utils/configEditor/Makefile.am, utils/logPlayer/Makefile.am, utils/makeConfig/Makefile.am, utils/notify/Makefile.am, utils/notifyObserver/Makefile.am, utils/nsIOR/Makefile.am, utils/policyController/Makefile.am, utils/policyEditor/Makefile.am, utils/qtJoystick/Makefile.am, utils/qtTouchPad/Makefile.am, utils/qtVideo/Makefile.am, utils/rangeSensor/Makefile.am, utils/sparrowBoard/Makefile.am, utils/widgets/Makefile.am, examples/b21Motion/Makefile.am, examples/battery/Makefile.am, examples/buttons/Makefile.am, examples/infrared/Makefile.am, examples/motion/Makefile.am, examples/notify/Makefile.am, examples/odometry/Makefile.am, examples/params/Makefile.am, examples/rangeSensor/Makefile.am, examples/robotikI/Makefile.am, examples/sonar/Makefile.am, examples/speechSimple/Makefile.am, examples/stall/Makefile.am, examples/video/Makefile.am, examples/videoFilter/Makefile.am, idl/Makefile.am, performance-tests/can/Makefile.am, performance-tests/faul/Makefile.am, performance-tests/logging/Makefile.am, performance-tests/mcp/Makefile.am, performance-tests/panTilt/Makefile.am, performance-tests/response/Makefile.am, performance-tests/video/Makefile.am, src/abus/Makefile.am, src/b21Base/Makefile.am, src/base/Makefile.am, src/buttons/Makefile.am, src/can/Makefile.am, src/faulMotor/Makefile.am, src/faulTty/Makefile.am, src/laser/Makefile.am, src/makeParams/Makefile.am, src/mcp/Makefile.am, src/miro/Makefile.am, src/msp/Makefile.am, src/panTilt/Makefile.am, src/params/Makefile.am, src/pioneer/Makefile.am, src/pioneerBase/Makefile.am, src/psos/Makefile.am:
	patches for all makefiles so that miro can be compiled using distcc

	I'm sorry about the mass of email, but note the effect (make -j20; built in the lab using 4 machines):
	standalone:  26m45.193s
	distcc:      14m53.863s

2004-12-14  Guillem Pages  <guillem@owl>

