2004-09-29  Hans Utz  <hutz@owl>

	* tests/log/LogTest.cpp: removing removed log categories

	* src/abus/AbusConnection.cpp, src/abus/AbusEventHandler.cpp, src/mcp/McpConnection.cpp, src/miro/Log.cpp, src/miro/Log.h, src/msp/MspMessage.h:
	removing some undocumented log categories and their usage in source code

	* src/video/VideoDevice1394.cpp, src/video/VideoDeviceQuickCam.cpp:
	minor include cleanup

	* utils/logPlayer/LogFile.cpp, utils/logPlayer/LogFile.h:
	propagating chanes from new log format
	also removed some debug output, there are no bugs left anyways :-)

	* utils/notify/LogNotify.cpp: added support for the Log.h

	* src/miro/Log.cpp, src/miro/LogHeader.h, src/miro/LogNotifyConsumer.cpp, src/miro/LogReader.cpp, src/miro/LogReader.h, src/miro/LogTypeRepository.cpp, src/miro/LogWriter.cpp, src/miro/LogWriter.h, src/miro/OdometryImpl.cpp:
	LogReader/TypeRepository/Writer/Header/NofifyConsumer:
	The next version of the event logging framework.
	this time we eliminate the need for splitting up the log file into two files
	the tcr is now appended instead of prepended.
	A new version of log truncate is currently missing, though.

	Log.cpp: Changing the category names according to documentation.
	OdometryImpl.cpp: using the LOG* macros for output

	* doc/tex/logging.tex: specification update :-)

	* src/miro/Log.h: committing changes for consistency with documentation

	* doc/tex/behaviourEngine.tex, doc/tex/blank.tex, doc/tex/event_channel_logging.tex, doc/tex/group_communication.tex, doc/tex/logging.tex, doc/tex/miro_manual.tex, doc/tex/parameters.tex, doc/tex/video.tex:
	Added some documentation on the ACE_Log_Msg based logging facility.
	Additionally added a chapter about the notify multicast module
	as well as the event channel based logging facilities. - But those are
	currently not populated with meaningfull content.
	Also committing an update on the configuarion/parameter handling chapter.
	This is mostly work in progress.

