/LogVideo.cpp, examples/video/Makefile, examples/video/Makefile.am, examples/video/Makefile.in, examples/video/VideoExample.cpp, examples/videoFilter/GrayVideoService.cpp, examples/videoFilter/Makefile, examples/videoFilter/Makefile.am, examples/videoFilter/Makefile.in, idl/Makefile, idl/Makefile.am, idl/Makefile.in, lib/Makefile.am, lib/Makefile.in, performance-tests/Makefile, performance-tests/Makefile.am, performance-tests/Makefile.in, performance-tests/can/Makefile, performance-tests/can/Makefile.am, performance-tests/can/Makefile.in, performance-tests/mcp/Makefile, performance-tests/mcp/Makefile.am, performance-tests/mcp/Makefile.in, performance-tests/panTilt/Makefile, performance-tests/panTilt/Makefile.am, performance-tests/panTilt/Makefile.in, performance-tests/panTilt/PanLatency.cpp, performance-tests/response/Makefile, performance-tests/response/Makefile.am, performance-tests/response/Makefile.in, performance-tests/response/NotifyResponse.cpp, performance-tests/response/PollResponse.cpp, performance-tests/video/GrabImages.cpp, performance-tests/video/Makefile, performance-tests/video/Makefile.am, performance-tests/video/Makefile.in, scripts/Makefile.am, scripts/Makefile.in, src/Makefile, src/Makefile.am, src/Makefile.in, src/abus/Makefile, src/abus/Makefile.am, src/abus/Makefile.in, src/b21Base/Makefile, src/b21Base/Makefile.am, src/b21Base/Makefile.in, src/base/BaseConnection.h, src/base/BaseDummyImpl.h, src/base/BaseImpl.h, src/base/BaseStatus.h, src/base/Makefile, src/base/Makefile.am, src/base/Makefile.in, src/buttons/ButtonsConnection.cpp, src/buttons/ButtonsConnection.h, src/buttons/ButtonsEventHandler.cpp, src/buttons/ButtonsEventHandler.h, src/buttons/ButtonsImpl.h, src/buttons/Makefile, src/buttons/Makefile.am, src/buttons/Makefile.in, src/can/Makefile, src/can/Makefile.am, src/can/Makefile.in, src/faulMotor/FaulMotorConsumer.h, src/faulMotor/FaulMotorMotionImpl.h, src/faulMotor/Makefile, src/faulMotor/Makefile.am, src/faulMotor/Makefile.in, src/faulTty/FaulTtyConnection.cpp, src/faulTty/Makefile, src/faulTty/Makefile.am, src/faulTty/Makefile.in:
	well, this damn huge commit is our swap to the new standard automake/autoconf (and libtool) gnu build system.
	if somethings not working properly, please look into the README or the normal tex-documentation

