	* src/miro/ConfigDocument.cpp: removing path from local includes

	* examples/videoFilter/Makefile:
	fixing dependency bug for autogenerated files

	* examples/video/.cvsignore, tests/videoBroker/.cvsignore, utils/logPlayer/.cvsignore, utils/widgets/.cvsignore:
	cleaning up cvsignore files

	* doc/tex/video.tex: fixing documentation and latex typos

	* etc/eve.xml: fixed missing section

	* utils/qtVideo/MainForm.cpp: debug output

	* tests/Makefile: adding the video broker test

	* tests/videoBroker/Makefile, tests/videoBroker/VideoBrokerTest.cpp:
	added a test for the video broker interface

	* examples/Makefile, examples/video/VideoExample.cpp, examples/videoFilter/FilterGray.cpp, examples/videoFilter/FilterGray.h, examples/videoFilter/GrayVideoService.cpp, examples/videoFilter/GrayVideoService.xml, examples/videoFilter/Makefile:
	propagating changes from big video service update
	added documentation stuff

	* idl/Video.idl: some more work on video broker interface

	* src/video/BufferManager.cpp, src/video/BufferManager.h, src/video/BufferManager1394.cpp, src/video/BufferManager1394.h, src/video/BufferManagerBTTV.cpp, src/video/BufferManagerBTTV.h, src/video/BufferManagerMeteor.cpp, src/video/BufferManagerMeteor.h, src/video/Makefile.bin, src/video/Makefile.lib, src/video/Parameters.xml, src/video/VideoAVDevice.h, src/video/VideoBrokerImpl.cpp, src/video/VideoBrokerImpl.h, src/video/VideoConsumer.cpp, src/video/VideoConsumer.h, src/video/VideoDevice.cpp, src/video/VideoDevice.h, src/video/VideoDevice1394.cpp, src/video/VideoDevice1394.h, src/video/VideoDeviceBTTV.cpp, src/video/VideoDeviceBTTV.h, src/video/VideoDeviceDummy.cpp, src/video/VideoDeviceDummy.h, src/video/VideoDeviceMeteor.cpp, src/video/VideoDeviceMeteor.h, src/video/VideoFilter.cpp, src/video/VideoFilter.h, src/video/VideoFilterBasic.cpp, src/video/VideoFilterBasic.h, src/video/VideoFilterLink.h, src/video/VideoImpl.cpp, src/video/VideoImpl.h, src/video/VideoServer.cpp, src/video/VideoServer.h:
	big video service update
	we now support filters with multiple input buffers
	we also support the first version of a video broker interface for
	synchronised image access and filter tree monitoring
	- it is not yet implementation complete...
	we now release buffers for reading as soon as all processing is done
	we now free buffers as soon as all successors are done
	added buffer manager for the individual devices
	connection management is now thread safe (at least has one severe bug less)
	TODO: documentation update
	TODO: video broker impl
	TODO: multiple devices

	* src/miro/TimeSeries.h:
	added a time series ring buffer for performance monitoring

	* src/miro/NotifyMulticastConfig.h: added missing include

