akeConfig.cpp, utils/makeConfig/Makefile, utils/makeConfig/PioneerDefaults, utils/makeConfig/PpbDefaults, utils/makeConfig/SparrowDefaults, utils/notify/.cvsignore, utils/notify/LogNotify.cpp, utils/notify/LogNotifyConsumer.cpp, utils/notify/LogNotifyConsumer.h, utils/notify/Makefile, utils/notify/Parameters.xml, utils/policyController/Makefile, utils/policyController/PolicyController.cpp, utils/policyController/PolicyController.h, utils/policyEditor/.cvsignore, utils/policyEditor/ArbiterWidget.cpp, utils/policyEditor/ArbiterWidget.h, utils/policyEditor/BehaviourDescription.h, utils/policyEditor/BehaviourParam.h, utils/policyEditor/BehaviourWidget.cpp, utils/policyEditor/BehaviourWidget.h, utils/policyEditor/ConfigDialog.cpp, utils/policyEditor/ConfigDialog.h, utils/policyEditor/Makefile, utils/policyEditor/ParamDialog.cpp, utils/policyEditor/ParamDialog.h, utils/policyEditor/ParameterDialog.cpp, utils/policyEditor/ParameterDialog.h, utils/policyEditor/PatternWidget.cpp, utils/policyEditor/PatternWidget.h, utils/policyEditor/PolicyArbiter.cpp, utils/policyEditor/PolicyArbiter.h, utils/policyEditor/PolicyBehaviour.cpp, utils/policyEditor/PolicyBehaviour.h, utils/policyEditor/PolicyConfig.cpp, utils/policyEditor/PolicyConfig.h, utils/policyEditor/PolicyConfigurationDialog.cpp, utils/policyEditor/PolicyConfigurationDialog.h, utils/policyEditor/PolicyDocument.cpp, utils/policyEditor/PolicyDocument.h, utils/policyEditor/PolicyEditor.cpp, utils/policyEditor/PolicyEditor.h, utils/policyEditor/PolicyPattern.cpp, utils/policyEditor/PolicyPattern.h, utils/policyEditor/PolicyView.cpp, utils/policyEditor/PolicyView.h, utils/policyEditor/test, utils/qtJoystick/Makefile, utils/qtTouchPad/Makefile, utils/qtVideo/Makefile, utils/rangeSensor/Makefile, utils/sparrowBoard/README, utils/sparrowBoard/SparrowAccel.cpp:
	big parameters architecture branch merging
	this patch provides parameter auto code generation for
	paramter files and behaviour parameter files
	the behaviour editor is much improved
	it handles now multiple behaviour config files
	it uses default dialogs where possible
	it has a strictly type safe behaviour parameter dialog
	it has a bubble help on types and default values in the bpd
	it has some segfaults fixed
	it has a mach speed improved redraw
	it has scaled scroll bars
	all parameter files are replace by parameter description files
	the changes were propagated through the entire project
	test cases for parameters and parameter descriptions and config files
	were added
	the sample behaviours are reorganized and cleaned up
	the miro_manual has a chapter about the new paramter code generation
	framework
	the behaviour chapter has been improved

