2002-12-10  Hans Utz  <hutz@owl>

	* utils/qtVideo/README: another readme

	* src/miro/BehaviourEngineImpl.h: added accessor methods for the policy

	* idl/BehaviourEngine.idl, src/base/BaseDevice.h, src/miro/ActionPattern.cpp, src/miro/ActionPattern.h, src/miro/Arbiter.cpp, src/miro/Arbiter.h, src/miro/ArbiterParameters.cpp, src/miro/ArbiterParameters.h, src/miro/Behaviour.cpp, src/miro/Behaviour.h, src/miro/BehaviourEngineImpl.cpp, src/miro/BehaviourEngineImpl.h, src/miro/BehaviourParameters.cpp, src/miro/BehaviourParameters.h, src/miro/EventBehaviour.cpp, src/miro/OdometryImpl.cpp, src/miro/Policy.cpp, src/miro/Policy.h, src/miro/PriorityArbiter.cpp, src/miro/PriorityArbiter.h, src/miro/TaskBehaviour.cpp, src/miro/TaskBehaviour.h, src/miro/TimedBehaviour.cpp, src/miro/TimedBehaviour.h, src/sparrow/SparrowDevice.h, tests/gripper/GripperTest.cpp, utils/policyController/PolicyController.cpp, utils/policyController/PolicyController.h:
	revamp of the behaviour framework
	added an interface to change behaviour parameters within a running policy
	- cleaned up the static variables to enable multiple policies
	- added a pointer to policy to every action pattern
	- added a pointer to action pattern in arbiter and behaviour parameters
	- added global transitions to the behaviour engine (IDL) and policy
	- added behaviour parameter get/set to the behaviour engine (IDL) and policy
	- added the new interface capabilities to the PolicyController
	propagated the changes through the existing behaviours
	- moved the factory methods for behaviour parameters into a macro
	added a testcase for the dynamic policy parameter changing

	enforcing normedness of orientation angles within the OdometryImpl
	- assert within OdometryImpl
	- fixes for B21, Pioneer and Sparrow to get it normalized
	  in the first place (BaseDevice, PioneerDevice, SparrowDevice)

	fixed the abort of the gripper test on move timed

