	* src/miro/Arbiter.cpp, src/miro/Arbiter.h, src/miro/ArbiterMessage.cpp, src/miro/ArbiterMessage.h, src/miro/ArbiterParameters.h, src/miro/ArbiterRepository.cpp, src/miro/ArbiterRepository.h, src/miro/Behaviour.cpp, src/miro/Behaviour.h, src/miro/BehaviourParameters.cpp, src/miro/BehaviourParameters.h, src/miro/BehaviourRepository.cpp, src/miro/BehaviourRepository.h, src/miro/Makefile.Miro, src/miro/Makefile.MiroSvc, src/miro/MotionArbiter.h, src/miro/MotionArbiterMessage.h, src/miro/Policy.cpp, src/miro/Policy.h, src/miro/Singleton.h:
	updates for inline documentation

	* tests/rangeSensor/.cvsignore: added missing cvsignore files

	* tests/Makefile: started a test suite for the behaviour stuff
	- added a PriorityArbiterTest with two multiply instancable dummy behaviours
	  and a multiply instanceable dummy arbiter

	* src/miro/ActionPattern.cpp, src/miro/ActionPattern.h, src/miro/Arbiter.cpp, src/miro/Arbiter.h, src/miro/ArbiterMessage.cpp, src/miro/ArbiterMessage.h, src/miro/ArbiterParameters.cpp, src/miro/ArbiterParameters.h, src/miro/Makefile.Miro, src/miro/MotionArbiter.cpp, src/miro/MotionArbiter.h, src/miro/MotionArbiterMessage.cpp, src/miro/MotionArbiterMessage.h, src/miro/MotionArbiterParameters.cpp, src/miro/MotionArbiterParameters.h, src/miro/MotionArbiterPower.cpp, src/miro/MotionArbiterPower.h, src/miro/Policy.cpp, src/miro/Policy.h, src/miro/PowerArbiter.cpp, src/miro/PowerArbiter.h, src/miro/PowerArbiterMessage.cpp, src/miro/PowerArbiterMessage.h, src/miro/PriorityArbiter.cpp, src/miro/PriorityArbiter.h, src/miro/WindowArbiter.cpp, src/miro/WindowArbiter.h, src/miro/WindowArbiterMessage.cpp, src/miro/WindowArbiterMessage.h, src/miro/WindowArbiterParameters.cpp, src/miro/WindowArbiterParameters.h:
	big revamp of the behaviour engine
	- moving the action pattern switching code from MotionArbiter to Arbiter
	- seperating the priority arbitration code from MotionArbiter into
	  the new PriorityArbiter super class
	- adding a PowerArbiter that as another descendant of the PriorityArbiter
	  for use with the Sparrow99 goalie
	- removing the never finished MotionArbiterPower
	- fixing the WindowArbiter code to work with the new arbiter infrastructur
	- made the arbiter message subclassable and move the VelocityIDL back into
	  the MotionArbiterMessage
	- Added PowerArbiterMessage as another ArbiterMessage subclass that holds the
	  left and right wheel power for the PowerArbiter

